{
  "stem": "24364.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were quite a few sick people that we had brought with us, which really was sickness still from the Atlantic, obviously.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at least 100 people were immediately hospitalized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I forgot to mention that there were-- I think we were like 1,500 people who got onto Mauritius.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "About 100 people were hospitalized immediately with the definite suspicion of typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I belonged, obviously, to the people who didn't have a profession and really didn't know anything except for a little field work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I decided I would like to help at the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were asking for volunteers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so a friend of mine and I decided that we'll give it a try.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had never, obviously, worked with sick people, and never worked in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were definitely needed, and so we started working with the hospitalized people, who most of them had typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was pretty rough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were-- the hospital, I forgot also to mention, was about-- was within the camp grounds and was about probably maybe 500 yards away from the main camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So in the morning, we had to usually go there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We needed the permission to leave the women's camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But obviously, it was granted to go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we worked there, if I remember correctly, like I think 8 to 10 hour shifts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And our main duties were feeding the patients, giving them a bedpan, and washing them, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We-- it was very, very sad to work at that hospital because so many people died.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
